      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Top, tail (no need to peel!) and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong> into a very large bowl</p><p>Chop<strong> </strong>your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> roughly and add them to the bowl</p>",
