      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Chop your<strong> paneer</strong> into bite-sized cubes</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> cubed paneer</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 3 min, turning once halfway, until golden</p>",
