    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the paneer is cooking, combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>mango chutney</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>mango dressing</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 5,
